k, hasn\u2019t had the most dazzling of years. In fairness, up until October, KLAC</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/172169690/image_172169690.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743135-kla-corporation-stock-still-not-good-buy-for-2025-reiterate-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 04:18:19"}, {"id": "4743133", "title": "XMHQ: A Strong Play In The Upcoming Lower Rate Environment", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman using pen to tick mark for check review and approve virtual document , Quality assurance and ISO concept.\" data-id=\"1917091208\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"802px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Dilok Klaisataporn</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>ETF Overview</h2> <p>Invesco S&amp;P MidCap Quality ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XMHQ\" title=\"Invesco S&amp;P MidCap Quality ETF\">XMHQ</a></span>) invests in a portfolio of about 80 quality mid-cap stocks selected from the S&amp;P 400 Mid-Cap Index. The fund has a high expense ratio of 0.25%. This is slightly higher than</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917091208/image_1917091208.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743133-xmhq-etf-strong-play-upcoming-lower-rate-environment", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 04:05:32"}, {"id": "4743132", "title": "Tracking George Soros's 13F Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Golden British pound sign breaks an ancient bank building into halves. Illustration of the concept of the impact and crisis of falling price of UK sterling\" data-id=\"1451506045\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dragon Claws</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of a series that provides an ongoing analysis of the changes made to George Soros\u2019s 13F stock portfolio on a quarterly basis. It is based on George Soros\u2019s regulatory <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1029160/000090266424006588/0000902664-24-006588-index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">13F Form</a> filed on</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1451506045/image_1451506045.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743132-tracking-george-soross-13f-portfolio-q3-2024-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 03:55:14"}, {"id": "4743128", "title": "Time Is Up For Tempus AI With IPO Lockup Expiration", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213764535/image_1213764535.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Data analyzing in commodities energy market: the charts and quotes on display. US WTI crude oil price analysis. Stunning price drop for the last 20 years.\" data-id=\"1213764535\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5760px\" height=\"3840px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213764535/image_1213764535.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213764535/image_1213764535.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1213764535/image_1213764535.jpg?io=getty-c-w1