-be-cautious-when-others-are-no-longer-fearful", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 03:04:47"}, {"id": "4743126", "title": "Asana: Stickiness Of AI Studio Could Lead The Turnaround - Initiating With Buy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The Passion of One Ignites New Ideas, Social Movements, Change\" data-id=\"155380391\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JamesBrey/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We're initiating our coverage on Asana, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASAN\" title=\"Asana, Inc.\">ASAN</a></span>) with a Buy after its recent <a href=\"https://investors.asana.com/financials/quarterly-results\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://investors.asana.com/financials/quarterly-results\" target=\"_blank\">3QFY25</a> earnings triggered the stock to close 43% higher the day after, on Friday, with Wall Street taking notice of Asana's new AI Studio and 89% gross profit</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155380391/image_155380391.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743126-asana-stickiness-of-ai-studio-could-lead-the-turnaround-initiating-with-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 02:41:31"}, {"id": "4743129", "title": "Opposite Day To Start The Week", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Calculator and charts\" data-id=\"160616076\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">deepblue4you</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>If you've had a good year so far in the stock market, chances are you had a pretty bad day in the market today. On the surface, today's action wasn't awful. The S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a>) was down</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/160616076/image_160616076.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743129-opposite-day-to-start-week", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 02:35:00"}, {"id": "4743124", "title": "Airbnb: Tough Road Ahead As Hotel Competitors Close In With Strong Bookings", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wide shot of smiling female friends relaxing on deck of luxury hotel suite at sunset\" data-id=\"1363844060\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/image_1363844060.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363844060/